FBIS3-12324 "drnes039_l_94018" FBIS-NES-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 ISRAEL Government Imposes Curfew, Closure of West Bank, Gaza Curfew Throughout West Bank TA2702104494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1000 GMT 27 Feb 94 TA2702104494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] The security forces have imposed a curfew on all Judaea and Samaria towns. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports that the curfew was clamped down on Nabulus, Qalqilyah, Ramallah, and Bethlehem, as well as their environs. The curfew on Hebron and its environs is continuing, and currently over 600,000 Palestinians in the territories are under curfew . Our correspondent Yo'av Aviv reports that security prisoners are currently rioting at the Megiddo prison in protest against the Hebron massacre.
